[4] Iran: 88 194 total cases, 5574 deaths
Date: Fri 24 Apr 2020 12:08 PM
Source: The Algemeiner, Reuters report [edited]
https://www.algemeiner.com/2020/04/24/iran-coronavirus-death-toll-rises-by-93-to-5574-health-official/


Iran's death toll from the new coronavirus rose by 93 on Friday [24 Apr 2020], to reach a total of 5574, Health Ministry spokesman Kianush Jahanpur said on state TV.

The total number of people diagnosed with the disease is 88 194, of whom 3121 are in critical condition, he added.

